high_descs: Turn around and go to the middle of the counter on the left.
Pick up the ladle on the counter.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Place the ladle inside the brown bowl.
Take the bowl with the ladle in it out of the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the counter on the left of the stove.
Place the bowl with the ladle in it in the right cabinet below the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move the bowl and ladle from the refrigerator to the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and hang a left at the black fridge to reach the counter.
Pick up the spoon with the black handle on the counter to the left of the loaf of bread.
Turn around and walk to the fridge ahead.
Open the fridge and put the spoon inside the brown bowl on the top shelf on the right side.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon from inside the fridge and close the door.
Turn around and cross the room to reach the cabinets under the counter next to the white stove.
Open the lower right cabinet, put the bowl with the spoon inside the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a spoon inside a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn completely around, walk forward a bit, then make a left to walk over to the counter space where the ladle and egg are.
Pick up the ladle that is on the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the refrigerator.
Place the ladle inside the bowl that is in the fridge.
Take the bowl with the ladle out of the fridge and close the door.
Turn around and walk back towards the counter space that is across from you.
Place the bowl with the ladle inside of the lower cabinet that is to the left of the stove and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled bowl with a ladle inside to a cabinet.
